::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike takes the printout and opens his mouth to reply, but 
Snitch runs off before he can say anything. The Alliance bot blinks, 
turning around and launching off again, wondering if the EMP field 
around this place affected neural circuitry or if it was just the bot 
himself.

He reaches the EMP field, waiting for his weapons to be returned to 
him.
